##What goes into each “bin” (quick refresher)

src/: reusable Python modules (e.g., src/analysis/light_shadow.py, src/models/clip_index.py)

notebooks/: experiments & EDA (01_explore.ipynb, 02_baselines.ipynb)

app/: your Streamlit files (app/app.py, app/components.py)

tests/: pytest files (tests/test_clip_index.py)

docs/: images, diagrams, demo GIF (docs/demo.gif)

data/raw, data/processed, models/: local artifacts (gitignored)

README.md: project overview for others

JOURNAL.md: your ongoing log
Write today's journal: ./journal.sh "Your goal for today"


Flow
1. create issue
2. work
3. commit
4. Done

